title: This Biscuit-Topped Chicken Pot Pie Is the Ultimate Cozy Winter Dish
text:
This Biscuit-Topped Chicken Pot Pie Is the Ultimate Cozy Winter Dish January 10, 2017 / 10:00 am By Munchies Staff 
Few dishes can combat cold weather like a chicken pot pie. 
With its buttery pie crust, rich stock, creamy roux, and juicy chicken, this dish that can satisfy even the most dire carb cravings and cold spells. But this recipe is even more decadent than your run-of-the-mill chicken pot pie, because it’s topped with biscuits. That’s right: goddamn biscuits on top of a chicken pot pie.
